and making false accusations.

00:02:06.040 --> 00:02:08.160
Colonel Sawa, that's going too far.

00:02:08.180 --> 00:02:09.250
Too far?

00:02:09.270 --> 00:02:09.690
Those corrupt officials
of the Nanjing government

00:02:09.690 --> 00:02:11.150
[No smoking or fire in the warehouse]

00:02:11.150 --> 00:02:13.410
smuggling behind your Japanese backs

00:02:13.410 --> 00:02:15.940
to line their own pockets—
isn't that common?

00:02:19.250 --> 00:02:20.650
Even if Colonel Sawa doesn't believe it,

00:02:20.650 --> 00:02:23.140
Wang Qizheng's signature can't be fake.

00:02:23.170 --> 00:02:23.860
If you want,

00:02:23.860 --> 00:02:23.900
[No smoking or fire in the warehouse]

00:02:23.900 --> 00:02:26.210
you can verify the handwriting.

00:02:28.930 --> 00:02:32.450
You've really set up a good trap.

00:02:33.650 --> 00:02:35.030
But don't forget,

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:36.640
Lin Nianci

00:02:37.060 --> 00:02:38.190
will soon bring

00:02:38.190 --> 00:02:40.520
the prisoners and confessions
from Zhongshan.

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:42.940
No matter what tricks you and He Xian try,

00:02:42.970 --> 00:02:44.500
once the witnesses arrive,

00:02:45.780 --> 00:02:47.450
your scheme will fall apart.

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:49.600
[No smoking or fire in the warehouse]

00:02:49.600 --> 00:02:50.410
Chief,

00:02:50.810 --> 00:02:51.670
I have a report.

00:02:51.900 --> 00:02:52.900
What is it? Speak!

00:02:57.110 --> 00:02:59.850
Something happened in Zhongshan.

00:03:07.410 --> 00:03:09.560
After a joint investigation
by Portuguese and Japanese authorities,

00:03:09.560 --> 00:03:11.220
the Steamship Sai On incident

00:03:11.290 --> 00:03:14.070
was solely caused by Lin Nianci,
an official of the Nanjing government,

00:03:14.070 --> 00:03:17.200
colluding with Wang Qizheng,
a corrupt Macau merchant, for smuggling.

00:03:17.200 --> 00:03:19.940
The Japanese case officer, Sawa Eisaku,

00:03:19.970 --> 00:03:21.150
at the time of the incident,

00:03:21.150 --> 00:03:22.530
used force without authorization,

00:03:22.530 --> 00:03:25.660
injuring many Macau police officers
and civilians.

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:27.860
During the investigation,
without verification,

00:03:27.860 --> 00:03:29.280
he deliberately distorted facts,

00:03:29.280 --> 00:03:30.480
provoked incidents,

00:03:30.480 --> 00:03:34.010
and even attempted to force
a prominent Macau businessman,

00:03:34.040 --> 00:03:35.900
Mr. He Xian, to give false testimony,

00:03:35.900 --> 00:03:38.079
falsely accusing the Macau government
of violating neutrality

00:03:38.079 --> 00:03:39.660
and participating in smuggling.

00:03:39.660 --> 00:03:40.640
In conclusion,

00:03:40.870 --> 00:03:43.260
we hereby issue a formal note

00:03:43.300 --> 00:03:45.240
to the Japanese government

00:03:45.240 --> 00:03:46.640
and the Southern China
Expeditionary Army Command

00:03:46.640 --> 00:03:47.670
making the following demands.

00:03:47.670 --> 00:03:48.370
First,

00:03:48.390 --> 00:03:50.070
the immediate return of Steamship Sai On.

00:03:50.070 --> 00:03:50.670
Second,

00:03:50.720 --> 00:03:53.930
reasonable compensation
for the injured Macau police

00:03:53.950 --> 00:03:55.300
and civilians at the pier.

00:03:55.300 --> 00:03:55.860
Third,

00:03:56.100 --> 00:03:58.460
termination of the Portuguese-Japanese
joint anti-smuggling agreement

00:03:58.460 --> 00:04:01.430
and cancellation of Japan's armed
anti-smuggling rights in Macau.

00:04:01.430 --> 00:04:01.980
Fourth,

00:04:02.190 --> 00:04:03.490
a formal apology

00:04:03.510 --> 00:04:06.300
to the Macau government

00:04:06.300 --> 00:04:07.650
and the falsely accused
innocent businessman, Mr. He Xian,

00:04:07.650 --> 00:04:11.310
with a guarantee that similar incidents
will never happen again.

00:04:18.930 --> 00:04:21.370
Our Command has confirmed

00:04:21.779 --> 00:04:24.070
that the entire Steamship Sai On incident

00:04:24.070 --> 00:04:26.150
was completely a misunderstanding.

00:04:26.280 --> 00:04:27.670
The Command accepts

00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:31.010
all demands made by your government.

00:04:31.360 --> 00:04:31.990
Now,

00:04:32.430 --> 00:04:34.560
on behalf of the Japanese government,

00:04:35.100 --> 00:04:36.690
I extend sincere apologies

00:04:37.010 --> 00:04:37.600
to the Macau government

00:04:37.600 --> 00:04:38.600
and

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:41.200
Mr. He Xian.

00:04:41.690 --> 00:04:44.810
We hope your government
will not harbor any grudges

00:04:45.260 --> 00:04:50.210
and continue to maintain
Japan-Portugal friendly cooperation.

00:05:03.280 --> 00:05:03.970
You.

00:05:10.880 --> 00:05:11.960
Colonel Sawa.

00:05:21.620 --> 00:05:23.350
Your Excellency the Governor,

00:05:24.590 --> 00:05:25.560
I'm sorry.

00:05:27.310 --> 00:05:29.200
Please accept my apology.

00:05:34.070 --> 00:05:34.870
Colonel Sawa,

00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:37.400
those you need to apologize to

00:05:37.420 --> 00:05:39.800
aren't just the Macau government.

00:06:10.880 --> 00:06:11.960
I'm sorry,

00:06:14.780 --> 00:06:15.680
Mr. He.

00:06:23.410 --> 00:06:25.290
Please forgive me.

