Hold it carefully.

00:07:32.570 --> 00:07:33.310
This way.

00:07:50.570 --> 00:07:51.100
Let's go.

00:08:26.410 --> 00:08:27.380
Haishan.

00:08:28.180 --> 00:08:29.180
-Commander!
-Yu.

00:08:30.100 --> 00:08:30.540
Commander!

