Commander, Haishan is awake!

00:08:37.200 --> 00:08:38.000
Haishan!

00:08:38.990 --> 00:08:39.900
You're awake.

00:08:42.580 --> 00:08:43.780
What's going on here?

00:08:44.770 --> 00:08:45.270
Well.

00:08:45.770 --> 00:08:47.080
I have good news for you.

00:08:47.080 --> 00:08:48.610
We just won a major victory.

00:08:48.960 --> 00:08:49.790
All these things

00:08:49.790 --> 00:08:51.390
are excellent equipment we've captured.

00:08:51.390 --> 00:08:54.010
We've crushed
all 4 enemy encirclement campaigns.

00:08:54.010 --> 00:08:56.000
-Yes, we've defeated them all.
-Yes, we've defeated them all.

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:58.350
The enemy has been driven out
of Black Hill!

00:08:58.350 --> 00:08:59.750
Right, they're all gone!

00:09:05.610 --> 00:09:08.130
Headquarters just

00:09:09.050 --> 00:09:11.000
sent transfer orders.

00:09:13.780 --> 00:09:15.560
I've been promoted.

00:09:15.580 --> 00:09:17.640
I'm to leave for Nanjing immediately

00:09:18.390 --> 00:09:21.990
to serve as Chief Advisor
to the Wang administration.

00:09:22.990 --> 00:09:25.320
Chief Advisor to the Nanjing government?

00:09:25.820 --> 00:09:27.960
Assigning such a nominal position

00:09:27.980 --> 00:09:31.180
is a promotion in name
but a demotion in reality, isn't it?

00:09:32.120 --> 00:09:33.550
Perhaps.

00:09:35.100 --> 00:09:37.520
Who can blame them
when this encirclement campaign

00:09:37.520 --> 00:09:39.450
was a complete failure?

00:09:39.780 --> 00:09:41.350
Over these past few years,

00:09:41.840 --> 00:09:45.670
our work in Macau has made no progress

00:09:45.690 --> 00:09:47.840
and suffered setback after setback.

00:09:49.090 --> 00:09:52.370
The fact that they still arranged
a Chief Advisor for me

00:09:52.850 --> 00:09:55.460
means they're cutting me some slack.

00:09:55.910 --> 00:09:56.740
General,

00:09:58.030 --> 00:09:59.270
I'm sorry.

00:10:00.170 --> 00:10:02.150
I was too careless this time,

00:10:02.930 --> 00:10:05.720
which led to the failure
of the Steamship Sai On operation.

00:10:05.720 --> 00:10:08.170
Command has already reached a conclusion.

00:10:08.960 --> 00:10:11.020
Regarding the Steamship Sai On case,

00:10:11.250 --> 00:10:12.360
this time, you

00:10:12.820 --> 00:10:14.960
successfully seized
a large amount of tungsten ore

00:10:14.960 --> 00:10:18.410
the Empire of Japan urgently needs,

00:10:18.770 --> 00:10:22.360
as well as an entire shipload of diesel.

00:10:23.110 --> 00:10:27.040
Even without a complete victory,
your achievements can't be ignored.

00:10:27.970 --> 00:10:33.040
This time,
I'll take responsibility for the failure

00:10:33.430 --> 00:10:37.180
to give you a chance
to turn things around in Macau.

00:10:43.630 --> 00:10:46.730
General Matsui will be replacing me.

00:10:48.530 --> 00:10:49.340
Sawa.

00:10:50.420 --> 00:10:52.080
I know that over the past year,

00:10:52.460 --> 00:10:58.830
you've been pushing for the Imperial Army
to directly occupy Macau.

00:10:59.960 --> 00:11:04.200
But General Matsui
firmly opposes this strategy.

00:11:04.760 --> 00:11:05.980
Despite your reluctance,

00:11:05.980 --> 00:11:09.120
you'll have to find another way.

00:11:10.130 --> 00:11:12.990
As for whether you
can make up for my disappointment

00:11:13.370 --> 00:11:14.700
and completely resolve

00:11:15.080 --> 00:11:18.760
the Macau issue for the Empire,

00:11:21.060 --> 00:11:22.420
that's up to you now.

00:11:26.270 --> 00:11:27.070
General,

00:11:28.040 --> 00:11:29.470
I assure you

00:11:31.100 --> 00:11:32.630
that I will spare no effort

00:11:32.630 --> 00:11:34.100
to thoroughly eradicate

00:11:34.980 --> 00:11:36.910
the anti-Japanese forces in Macau

00:11:38.260 --> 00:11:40.310
at all costs.

00:11:47.070 --> 00:11:48.340
I asked you here this time

00:11:48.340 --> 00:11:49.930
to repay a favor.

00:11:50.120 --> 00:11:52.360
A favor? What do you mean?

00:11:52.770 --> 00:11:55.100
Last time I asked you to put on an act
in front of Wang Qizheng,

00:11:55.100 --> 00:11:56.370
didn't I promise you

00:11:56.390 --> 00:11:58.190
that I'd help you make a fortune?

00:11:58.540 --> 00:11:59.900
It was nothing.

00:11:59.930 --> 00:12:02.060
Xian, you're taking it too seriously.

00:12:02.080 --> 00:12:03.650
Is your President Saito from Lyun Coeng

00:12:03.650 --> 00:12:05.320
going crazy lately,

00:12:05.320 --> 00:12:07.030
buying up supplies everywhere?

00:12:07.030 --> 00:12:08.680
He wants everything, no matter what it is.

00:12:08.680 --> 00:12:10.980
That's true. These Japanese

00:12:11.180 --> 00:12:12.290
have gone desperate.

00:12:12.290 --> 00:12:13.510
I heard that in their country,

00:12:13.510 --> 00:12:15.480
even cooking pots from ordinary homes

00:12:15.480 --> 00:12:17.180
and nails from the roof beams
have all been collected.

00:12:17.180 --> 00:12:19.380
So now, no matter what can be purchased,

00:12:19.380 --> 00:12:21.030
Saito is willing to pay top dollar.

00:12:21.030 --> 00:12:22.010
As long as one can get the goods,

00:12:22.010 --> 00:12:24.720
the company offers
frighteningly high commissions.

00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:25.650
That's perfect.

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:27.050
Recently, I've gathered

00:12:27.050 --> 00:12:29.140
inventory from all merchants across Macau.

00:12:29.140 --> 00:12:31.810
There are some machines,
equipment, instruments,

00:12:31.810 --> 00:12:33.010
and some small parts.

00:12:33.670 --> 00:12:35.460
But they're either too old

00:12:35.570 --> 00:12:36.790
or incomplete sets.

00:12:36.960 --> 00:12:39.230
Nobody elsewhere would want them.

00:12:39.340 --> 00:12:41.020
But I wonder if President Saito

00:12:41.020 --> 00:12:41.890
would mind.

00:12:41.920 --> 00:12:42.980
Mind? He wouldn't.

00:12:42.990 --> 00:12:44.570
Right now, for any metal products

00:12:44.570 --> 00:12:45.740
that can be melted down and reused,

00:12:45.740 --> 00:12:46.810
he'd be more than happy to take.

00:12:46.810 --> 00:12:47.610
Not to mention

00:12:47.620 --> 00:12:49.340
there are so many usable items there.

00:12:49.340 --> 00:12:50.170
But one thing,

00:12:50.170 --> 00:12:51.000
Xian,

00:12:51.690 --> 00:12:53.900
do you really plan
to sell them to the Japanese?

00:12:53.900 --> 00:12:55.190
Didn't you just say

00:12:55.300 --> 00:12:57.360
Saito offers such high commissions?

00:12:57.470 --> 00:12:59.000
Once this deal is done,

00:12:59.020 --> 00:12:59.650
the fortune I promised you

00:12:59.650 --> 00:13:01.840
will be yours.

00:13:03.060 --> 00:13:04.100
But, Xian,

00:13:05.290 --> 00:13:06.480
are you serious?

00:13:06.770 --> 00:13:08.300
You still don't believe me?

00:13:10.970 --> 00:13:12.110
However,

00:13:13.110 --> 00:13:14.310
I have one condition.

00:13:17.070 --> 00:13:17.960
Chairman,

00:13:17.980 --> 00:13:21.100
this is the list of supplies
I've recently acquired.

00:13:24.520 --> 00:13:26.240
Looks like quite a lot.

00:13:26.650 --> 00:13:27.590
Well done.

00:13:27.940 --> 00:13:28.870
Well done.

00:13:29.250 --> 00:13:30.530
You're too kind.

00:13:30.980 --> 00:13:34.190
Although the quantity is large this time,

00:13:34.220 --> 00:13:37.720
the equipment and parts are incomplete,

00:13:37.740 --> 00:13:40.610
and they cost a high price.

00:13:40.910 --> 00:13:42.840
Why worry about high prices?
Who cares if they're incomplete?

00:13:42.840 --> 00:13:43.680
These supplies,

00:13:43.680 --> 00:13:45.750
for factories back home
suffering from bombings,

00:13:45.750 --> 00:13:47.760
are as precious as gold.

00:13:47.780 --> 00:13:48.550
Manager He,

00:13:48.860 --> 00:13:50.810
you've done well.

00:13:50.930 --> 00:13:52.310
I'm giving you a bonus.

00:13:52.330 --> 00:13:53.260
One million.

00:13:53.360 --> 00:13:54.620
Thank you.

00:13:58.050 --> 00:13:59.290
However,

00:13:59.740 --> 00:14:02.120
what's urgent now

00:14:02.520 --> 00:14:05.230
is how to transport these supplies.

00:14:05.430 --> 00:14:06.740
As you know,

00:14:06.770 --> 00:14:09.890
all the merchant ships in Macau

00:14:09.910 --> 00:14:14.430
have been requisitioned by Command.

00:14:14.520 --> 00:14:18.660
We have no ocean transport capability now.

00:14:20.860 --> 00:14:26.830
Maybe there's a way
in Guangzhou or Hong Kong?

00:14:27.040 --> 00:14:27.270
[Lyun Coeng Freight]

00:14:27.270 --> 00:14:28.330
I just remembered.

00:14:29.020 --> 00:14:30.420
There's an opportunity.

00:14:30.850 --> 00:14:32.450
There are supplies
confiscated by Colonel Sawa

00:14:32.450 --> 00:14:34.420
in the Steamship Sai On incident.

00:14:34.450 --> 00:14:36.790
Headquarters has specifically
arranged a ship

00:14:36.790 --> 00:14:38.650
to transport them back home soon.

00:14:39.590 --> 00:14:42.060
Our Lyun Coeng shipment isn't that large.

00:14:42.270 --> 00:14:45.090
It would only take up a small corner
of the warehouse.

00:14:45.090 --> 00:14:45.140
But as you said,

00:14:45.140 --> 00:14:47.520
[Lyun Coeng Freight]

00:14:47.520 --> 00:14:50.950
they're shipping important supplies,
and ours...

00:14:51.290 --> 00:14:53.670
They are both crucial supplies
desperately needed back home.

00:14:53.670 --> 00:14:55.270
They're equally important.

00:14:55.890 --> 00:14:58.470
I'll call the Southern China
Expeditionary Army Command immediately

00:14:58.470 --> 00:14:59.830
to make the request.

00:14:59.850 --> 00:15:02.200
I'm sure they'll agree.

00:15:02.200 --> 00:15:02.760
[Lyun Coeng Freight]

00:15:02.760 --> 00:15:03.550
Manager He,

00:15:04.220 --> 00:15:05.580
start preparing right away.

00:15:05.580 --> 00:15:07.460
You must personally oversee

00:15:07.480 --> 00:15:09.620
the transfer of these goods
to Hong Kong for shipping.

00:15:09.620 --> 00:15:10.440
[Lyun Coeng Freight]

00:15:10.440 --> 00:15:11.010
Yes.

00:15:13.710 --> 00:15:17.130
This operation is top secret.
Proceed with extreme caution.

00:15:17.280 --> 00:15:18.950
Since it's top secret,

00:15:18.980 --> 00:15:20.330
upon arrival in Hong Kong,

00:15:20.330 --> 00:15:22.870
the loading time and details...

00:15:23.630 --> 00:15:26.010
I'll notify you personally.

00:15:26.390 --> 00:15:28.590
Yes, I'll make sure it's done properly.

00:16:04.910 --> 00:16:05.620
Come in.

00:16:08.680 --> 00:16:09.340
Father.

00:16:09.370 --> 00:16:10.090
Grandpa.

00:16:10.130 --> 00:16:10.910
I'm back.

00:16:10.940 --> 00:16:11.810
You're back.

00:16:18.770 --> 00:16:19.410
Father,

00:16:19.890 --> 00:16:20.670
I'm sorry.

00:16:21.010 --> 00:16:22.600
Why are you apologizing?

00:16:24.380 --> 00:16:25.740
I promised you before

00:16:26.120 --> 00:16:29.280
that you could use the dividends
from Tai Fung Bank to buy land.

00:16:29.280 --> 00:16:30.280
These days,

00:16:30.660 --> 00:16:31.870
you've been working hard

00:16:31.870 --> 00:16:33.220
finding properties.

00:16:34.590 --> 00:16:37.530
But I still donated that money
to the guerrilla unit.

00:16:43.780 --> 00:16:44.410
Zai,

00:16:45.410 --> 00:16:46.010
come here.

00:16:48.940 --> 00:16:49.850
Tell me.

00:16:51.310 --> 00:16:54.410
Why do I want to buy properties?

00:16:54.930 --> 00:16:58.530
So our family has assets and a foundation.

00:16:58.560 --> 00:16:59.320
Yes.

00:16:59.880 --> 00:17:03.100
A family must first
establish its foundation

00:17:03.330 --> 00:17:05.359
to give its members peace of mind.

00:17:05.839 --> 00:17:07.940
But as the old saying goes,

00:17:08.210 --> 00:17:10.880
wealth never survives 3 generations.

00:17:12.180 --> 00:17:13.599
And why is that?

00:17:14.869 --> 00:17:17.440
Because even with great wealth,

00:17:18.510 --> 00:17:19.550
you can't prevent

00:17:20.490 --> 00:17:22.060
unfilial descendants.

00:17:22.430 --> 00:17:24.970
If descendants can

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:26.300
know what to prioritize,

00:17:26.300 --> 00:17:27.560
understand the greater path,

00:17:27.560 --> 00:17:28.550
and put the greater good

00:17:28.550 --> 00:17:30.350
before personal interests

00:17:30.370 --> 00:17:32.340
and country before family,

00:17:33.710 --> 00:17:35.490
then why worry that this family

00:17:36.600 --> 00:17:38.320
won't prosper

00:17:38.890 --> 00:17:40.620
for generations?

00:17:41.950 --> 00:17:42.660
Zai.

00:17:43.300 --> 00:17:44.250
Tell me again.

00:17:45.840 --> 00:17:46.860
Did your father

00:17:46.890 --> 00:17:48.610
do the right thing

00:17:49.230 --> 00:17:50.440
to use the money that way?

00:17:50.440 --> 00:17:51.000
Yes.

00:17:51.390 --> 00:17:52.520
Why is that right?

00:17:52.540 --> 00:17:55.940
Because one should
prioritize the greater good

00:17:55.970 --> 00:17:57.700
and put country before family.

00:17:59.230 --> 00:17:59.750
Good.

00:18:00.020 --> 00:18:01.290
Well said.

00:18:03.210 --> 00:18:06.050
As long as you maintain this mindset
of prioritizing the greater good

00:18:06.050 --> 00:18:08.170
and putting country before family,

00:18:09.360 --> 00:18:10.950
I can rest easy.

00:18:14.860 --> 00:18:16.780
This is the true foundation

00:18:17.170 --> 00:18:18.150
of our He family,

00:18:18.690 --> 00:18:20.990
which no one can take away.

00:18:22.130 --> 00:18:24.610
As long as we hold onto this principle,

00:18:24.860 --> 00:18:26.230
our family will

00:18:26.250 --> 00:18:27.400
prosper.

00:18:28.030 --> 00:18:29.230
In the future, we will

00:18:29.250 --> 00:18:30.680
grow strong roots

00:18:31.150 --> 00:18:33.010
and benefit future generations.

00:18:38.460 --> 00:18:40.590
Let's offer incense to our ancestors.

00:18:40.740 --> 00:18:41.130
Come.

00:18:44.710 --> 00:18:50.690
[Memorial Tablet of the Ancestors
of the He Family in Panyu]

00:18:51.080 --> 00:18:56.790
[Memorial Tablet of the Ancestors
of the He Family in Panyu]

00:18:56.860 --> 00:18:59.650
He Xian, a descendant of the He family.

00:19:00.220 --> 00:19:01.180
I'm here.

00:19:01.990 --> 00:19:03.660
Before our ancestors,

00:19:04.150 --> 00:19:05.810
you shall answer truthfully.

00:19:06.380 --> 00:19:07.620
Throughout this day,

00:19:08.200 --> 00:19:10.540
were you ever dishonest
in your business dealings?

00:19:10.540 --> 00:19:11.450
No.

00:19:11.900 --> 00:19:12.770
Did you

00:19:13.250 --> 00:19:14.680
break any promises?

00:19:15.120 --> 00:19:16.210
No.

00:19:16.730 --> 00:19:17.930
As for other matters,

00:19:18.560 --> 00:19:19.820
have you

00:19:19.920 --> 00:19:21.610
lived up to

00:19:21.610 --> 00:19:21.940
[Memorial Tablet of the Ancestors
of the He Family in Panyu]

00:19:21.940 --> 00:19:23.640
the teachings of our ancestors

00:19:23.640 --> 00:19:25.250
with a clear conscience?

00:19:25.670 --> 00:19:27.040
I, He Xian, swear that I have yet to

00:19:27.040 --> 00:19:28.330
deviate from my duties.

00:19:28.330 --> 00:19:29.990
My conscience remains clear.

00:19:43.180 --> 00:19:48.120
[Memorial Tablet of the Ancestors
of the He Family in Panyu]

00:19:48.380 --> 00:19:48.980
Okay.

00:19:49.260 --> 00:19:49.800
Partner.

00:19:50.950 --> 00:19:51.810
Hurry back to Macau

00:19:51.810 --> 00:19:52.900
and be careful.

00:19:54.200 --> 00:19:55.930
Here's the news from Xiao Feng.

00:19:56.220 --> 00:19:58.480
The 2 Japanese ships
carrying our tungsten ore and diesel

00:19:58.480 --> 00:20:01.010
have already set sail
from the Hong Kong pier.

00:20:01.430 --> 00:20:03.690
Then hurry upstairs and send the message.

00:20:03.690 --> 00:20:04.880
Don't worry, Xian.

00:20:05.900 --> 00:20:08.490
The bomber squadron
is already on standby at the airport.

00:20:08.490 --> 00:20:10.280
None of them will escape.

00:20:10.300 --> 00:20:10.950
Ping,

00:20:10.980 --> 00:20:12.150
cover for me for a moment.

00:20:12.150 --> 00:20:12.910
Hurry up.

00:20:12.940 --> 00:20:13.680
Hurry.

00:20:13.810 --> 00:20:15.350
Who would've thought?

00:20:15.370 --> 00:20:16.900
After we suffered such a big loss,

00:20:16.900 --> 00:20:18.210
Xian would use a pile of junk

00:20:18.210 --> 00:20:19.570
to lure them out.

00:20:19.600 --> 00:20:21.340
Xian always has a plan.

00:20:21.970 --> 00:20:23.970
For all the tungsten ore and diesel,

00:20:23.980 --> 00:20:25.900
it would've been painful enough
to lose them ourselves,

00:20:25.900 --> 00:20:27.900
let alone letting those Japanese
have them.

00:20:27.900 --> 00:20:28.810
Dream on.

00:20:41.310 --> 00:20:48.550
[Hang Taai Mercearia]

00:20:50.120 --> 00:20:50.770
Kong it.

00:20:56.550 --> 00:20:57.710
I just got word

00:20:58.160 --> 00:20:59.680
that those 2 Japanese ships,

00:20:59.680 --> 00:21:02.020
boom, had been blown to bits!

00:21:04.640 --> 00:21:06.840
Win via Draw after Kong with Four Kongs!

00:21:08.030 --> 00:21:09.670
Isn't that a big hand?

00:21:12.900 --> 00:21:13.950
It's beautiful.

00:21:16.220 --> 00:21:17.110
Yes.

00:21:20.540 --> 00:21:21.230
Yinwan.

00:21:21.250 --> 00:21:21.820
Yes?

00:21:22.050 --> 00:21:23.370
When the war is over,

00:21:24.350 --> 00:21:26.280
what are your plans for the future?

00:21:26.920 --> 00:21:28.260
I've thought about it,

00:21:28.730 --> 00:21:30.190
but I haven't decided yet.

00:21:30.450 --> 00:21:31.510
But I have.

00:21:32.660 --> 00:21:34.090
After all this is over,

00:21:34.870 --> 00:21:36.650
I'll resign from the government

00:21:36.650 --> 00:21:38.100
and sell Bachongtian Club.

00:21:38.100 --> 00:21:38.730
Why?

00:21:40.590 --> 00:21:42.280
You've stayed at Bachongtian Club

00:21:42.280 --> 00:21:44.610
because you have something you want to do.

00:21:44.750 --> 00:21:46.060
I've always known

00:21:46.340 --> 00:21:48.420
that you long for a pure stage.

00:21:48.640 --> 00:21:49.690
Your violin

00:21:49.910 --> 00:21:51.350
should be played for those

00:21:51.350 --> 00:21:53.400
who truly appreciate music.

00:21:56.520 --> 00:21:58.500
I'm so tired after all these years.

00:21:59.050 --> 00:22:00.810
I want to leave all these disputes behind

00:22:00.810 --> 00:22:02.280
and fulfill my dream

00:22:02.860 --> 00:22:04.080
to establish

00:22:04.110 --> 00:22:04.940
a genuine,

00:22:04.960 --> 00:22:05.910
pure orchestra

00:22:06.480 --> 00:22:08.750
and return to the original purpose
of music.

00:22:08.750 --> 00:22:09.810
That's wonderful.

00:22:12.830 --> 00:22:13.360
Yinwan.

00:22:13.390 --> 00:22:13.830
Yes?

00:22:15.330 --> 00:22:17.190
Will you do this with me?

00:22:21.310 --> 00:22:22.780
In this war,

00:22:23.720 --> 00:22:26.560
many children have lost their families
and homes.

00:22:27.650 --> 00:22:29.550
After the war ends,

00:22:29.630 --> 00:22:30.900
I should return to the orphanage

00:22:30.900 --> 00:22:31.870
to help those children

00:22:31.870 --> 00:22:33.800
find hope in their lives again.

00:22:36.180 --> 00:22:36.910
Well then...

00:22:38.240 --> 00:22:39.440
Then I'll go with you.

00:22:40.490 --> 00:22:41.530
Whatever you do,

00:22:41.980 --> 00:22:43.060
I'll support you.

00:22:50.980 --> 00:22:51.950
Dr. Lok Pak.

00:22:52.840 --> 00:22:54.190
Actually, I think

00:22:55.940 --> 00:22:56.660
you should do

00:22:56.660 --> 00:22:58.230
what you truly want to do.

00:22:58.720 --> 00:22:59.120
I...

00:23:23.820 --> 00:23:27.600
[Chengxin Company Order]

00:23:30.250 --> 00:23:32.360
Getting so much cargo this time.

00:23:35.700 --> 00:23:37.200
When I first got the order,

00:23:37.240 --> 00:23:39.430
I didn't expect the quantity
to be so large.

00:23:39.430 --> 00:23:42.100
Mr. He and Mr. Ke's appetite

00:23:42.120 --> 00:23:43.780
is getting bigger and bigger.

00:23:44.800 --> 00:23:46.330
It's not about my appetite.

00:23:46.440 --> 00:23:48.040
The war situation is developing rapidly,

00:23:48.040 --> 00:23:49.640
and domestic demand is high.

00:23:49.730 --> 00:23:51.680
Ever since the bombers
from Zhijiang Airport

00:23:51.680 --> 00:23:53.890
could fly directly
to the Japanese homeland

00:23:53.890 --> 00:23:56.130
and drop bombs on their Imperial Palace,

00:23:56.130 --> 00:23:57.990
the Japanese have been panicked.

00:23:58.280 --> 00:23:59.250
Yang Chang's intelligence station

00:23:59.250 --> 00:24:01.040
has also received notice from above.

00:24:01.040 --> 00:24:02.000
They say the Japanese

00:24:02.000 --> 00:24:03.830
are desperately moving troops,

00:24:03.850 --> 00:24:06.580
preparing for a large-scale attack
on Zhijiang.

00:24:06.940 --> 00:24:09.840
Hundreds of thousands of national troops
are preparing to meet them head-on.

00:24:09.840 --> 00:24:13.240
The battle line is already far from
the Yunnan-Guizhou rear.

00:24:13.350 --> 00:24:14.410
Once the battle begins,

00:24:14.410 --> 00:24:16.650
relying on the Burma Road and the Hump

00:24:16.670 --> 00:24:18.800
for limited supplies won't be enough.

00:24:19.350 --> 00:24:20.180
So,

00:24:20.210 --> 00:24:22.230
the supplies coming through Macau
this time

00:24:22.230 --> 00:24:23.690
are more than ever before.

00:24:23.710 --> 00:24:24.510
That's right.

00:24:24.600 --> 00:24:25.820
And in North and Central China,

00:24:25.820 --> 00:24:27.370
taking advantage
of the enemy's vulnerable rear,

00:24:27.370 --> 00:24:28.820
the Eighth Route Army
and the New Fourth Army

00:24:28.820 --> 00:24:30.970
are also about to launch
a full counteroffensive.

00:24:30.970 --> 00:24:32.180
The supply gap is significant,

00:24:32.180 --> 00:24:33.780
so we've asked Mr. Rodrigues

00:24:33.800 --> 00:24:35.030
to help with the procurement.

00:24:35.030 --> 00:24:36.010
Excellent.

00:24:36.460 --> 00:24:37.900
The day we have long awaited—

00:24:37.900 --> 00:24:40.430
the counteroffensive—has finally arrived.

00:24:40.770 --> 00:24:43.440
I think the goods
will arrive in a day or two.

00:24:43.830 --> 00:24:46.000
You'll need to prepare more manpower;

00:24:46.170 --> 00:24:47.600
otherwise,

00:24:48.020 --> 00:24:49.810
I won't be able to unload everything.

00:24:49.810 --> 00:24:51.330
Luo, don't worry.

00:24:51.670 --> 00:24:52.920
However many people you need,

00:24:52.920 --> 00:24:54.640
I'll send them to you.

00:24:54.920 --> 00:24:55.360
Good.

00:24:55.490 --> 00:24:56.140
Also,

00:24:56.160 --> 00:24:58.160
the Japanese anti-smuggling rights
in Macau

00:24:58.160 --> 00:24:59.290
have been canceled,

00:24:59.290 --> 00:25:01.690
but this shipment is extremely important.

00:25:01.750 --> 00:25:02.900
Better safe than sorry.

00:25:02.900 --> 00:25:04.020
So when the time comes,

00:25:04.020 --> 00:25:05.220
we'll all keep watch at the pier.

00:25:05.220 --> 00:25:05.650
Yeah.

00:25:05.920 --> 00:25:06.360
Sure.

00:25:06.670 --> 00:25:08.640
I'll have Gonçalves
send more Portuguese police

00:25:08.640 --> 00:25:10.190
and find a reason to secure the pier

00:25:10.190 --> 00:25:12.320
to ensure the safety of this shipment.

00:25:20.830 --> 00:25:22.610
This is also it.

00:25:40.820 --> 00:25:41.980
Mr. Fukue!

00:25:43.350 --> 00:25:44.600
Look at these.

00:25:46.340 --> 00:25:48.010
I've gathered all the investigation
and surveillance information

00:25:48.010 --> 00:25:50.320
about anti-Japanese forces in Macau

00:25:50.350 --> 00:25:54.220
from the past 3 years!

00:25:55.550 --> 00:25:57.340
I plan to compile

00:25:57.370 --> 00:25:58.970
a detailed analysis report,

00:25:59.130 --> 00:26:02.810
along with new recommendations
for Macau operations,

00:26:03.210 --> 00:26:05.470
to submit to Command as soon as possible.

00:26:06.870 --> 00:26:09.050
New recommendations for Macau operations?

00:26:09.050 --> 00:26:10.380
What recommendations?

00:26:11.160 --> 00:26:14.310
Of course, the armed occupation of Macau.

00:26:14.740 --> 00:26:16.140
What else could it be?

00:26:17.820 --> 00:26:18.640
Mr. Fukue.

00:26:19.560 --> 00:26:22.690
You know everything that's happened
these past 3 years.

00:26:23.110 --> 00:26:24.800
The entire Macau

00:26:24.940 --> 00:26:27.200
has been completely controlled by He Xian

00:26:27.200 --> 00:26:29.140
and anti-Japanese elements.

00:26:29.420 --> 00:26:32.300
The Anglo-American forces
have established contact with them,

00:26:32.300 --> 00:26:35.820
and the Portuguese Macau government
has joined their camp.

00:26:36.750 --> 00:26:40.170
If the Imperial Army deploys immediately
to occupy Macau,

00:26:40.900 --> 00:26:46.420
the Macau issue
can be completely resolved!

00:26:48.400 --> 00:26:50.490
Then why did you ask me to come?

00:26:51.770 --> 00:26:55.500
I want you to jointly submit
this proposal with me.

00:26:55.760 --> 00:26:59.210
General Matsui is very displeased with me

00:26:59.700 --> 00:27:02.960
and doesn't agree with
the military occupation strategy.

00:27:03.480 --> 00:27:07.180
I alone can't convince Command.

00:27:15.630 --> 00:27:16.280
Why?

00:27:20.280 --> 00:27:21.740
You don't want to co-sign?

00:27:22.470 --> 00:27:23.760
Well then,

00:27:24.710 --> 00:27:26.840
you can take the lead in submitting it,

00:27:26.880 --> 00:27:28.740
and I'll co-sign. That works too.

00:27:29.980 --> 00:27:32.180
It seems I do need to submit

00:27:32.200 --> 00:27:35.500
a formal written proposal to Command.

00:27:36.700 --> 00:27:38.360
That's more like it.

00:27:38.630 --> 00:27:40.630
I'll draft the report immediately.

00:27:41.370 --> 00:27:42.810
You'll just need to sign it.

00:27:42.810 --> 00:27:44.430
I'm submitting it myself,

00:27:45.030 --> 00:27:46.980
not jointly with you.

00:27:48.690 --> 00:27:50.140
Not jointly with me?

00:27:53.360 --> 00:27:54.320
Then what do you

00:27:55.370 --> 00:27:57.160
plan to recommend?

00:27:58.140 --> 00:27:59.540
I recommend that Command

00:28:00.780 --> 00:28:03.390
abolish the Sawa Agency.

00:28:13.870 --> 00:28:15.330
What are you thinking?

00:28:17.420 --> 00:28:19.200
Have you lost your mind?

00:28:19.220 --> 00:28:20.390
I'm not crazy!

00:28:21.150 --> 00:28:23.220
You are!

00:28:24.090 --> 00:28:25.770
Your sheer obstinacy

00:28:25.940 --> 00:28:27.760
has led to

00:28:28.850 --> 00:28:34.200
the irreversible situation in Macau.

00:28:34.960 --> 00:28:37.240
I did it all for the Empire,

00:28:38.260 --> 00:28:39.360
for the Sacred War,

00:28:41.790 --> 00:28:44.500
and for the Emperor!

00:28:44.500 --> 00:28:45.610
No!

00:28:46.570 --> 00:28:47.550
You simply

00:28:48.430 --> 00:28:51.260
can't accept defeat!

00:28:52.350 --> 00:28:54.460
Ever since you were repeatedly
defeated by those Chinese merchants,

00:28:54.460 --> 00:28:56.660
especially by He Xian,

00:28:57.850 --> 00:28:58.700
Sawa,

00:28:59.130 --> 00:29:01.220
you've gone mad!

00:29:01.860 --> 00:29:03.790
You're escalating the situation.

00:29:04.770 --> 00:29:06.220
Even when the Imperial Army

00:29:06.220 --> 00:29:08.090
is in such an unfavorable position,

00:29:08.090 --> 00:29:11.290
you still want to use them
to occupy Macau!

00:29:22.850 --> 00:29:28.610
Your insane ideas

00:29:29.750 --> 00:29:32.750
have seriously jeopardized
the Empire's Sacred War.

00:29:33.140 --> 00:29:36.570
As the Consul in Macau,

00:29:37.090 --> 00:29:41.420
I must take responsibility
for the Empire's interests.

00:29:42.090 --> 00:29:42.750
Therefore,

00:29:43.750 --> 00:29:45.750
I will submit a report to Command,

00:29:46.880 --> 00:29:49.750
detailing all your actions
over the past 3 years

00:29:50.270 --> 00:29:52.330
with comprehensive documentation.

00:29:53.100 --> 00:29:56.750
I believe that once Command
receives my report,

00:29:57.240 --> 00:30:01.070
they'll take appropriate action
against Sawa Agency.

00:30:24.430 --> 00:30:27.490
Great. The goods have finally arrived.

00:30:29.900 --> 00:30:30.640
Chief.

00:30:31.070 --> 00:30:32.000
Chief.

00:30:44.750 --> 00:30:45.490
Chief.

00:30:45.630 --> 00:30:46.560
Are you alright?

00:30:51.670 --> 00:30:52.510
Chief,

00:30:52.760 --> 00:30:55.690
Captain Huang has important information
to report.

00:30:59.350 --> 00:31:00.030
Chief,

00:31:00.710 --> 00:31:02.530
we just discovered something important.

00:31:02.530 --> 00:31:03.630
At the inner harbor pier,

00:31:03.630 --> 00:31:04.800
Rodrigues' company

00:31:04.820 --> 00:31:07.080
has 2 large cargo ships that have docked.

00:31:08.250 --> 00:31:09.620
Since they started unloading,

00:31:09.620 --> 00:31:12.690
the Portuguese police have completely
sealed off the entire port.

00:31:12.690 --> 00:31:14.020
Nobody is allowed near.

00:31:14.030 --> 00:31:15.030
But the people unloading

00:31:15.030 --> 00:31:16.640
seem to all be
from the Tai Ho Brotherhood.

00:31:16.640 --> 00:31:18.630
Our people simply can't get close.

00:31:18.760 --> 00:31:19.460
Also,

00:31:20.150 --> 00:31:21.900
He Xian and his people were there too.

00:31:21.900 --> 00:31:23.950
They kept watch for 2 whole days

00:31:23.970 --> 00:31:25.230
while they were unloading the cargo.

00:31:25.230 --> 00:31:26.700
They didn't leave

00:31:26.720 --> 00:31:29.400
until all the goods were placed

00:31:29.430 --> 00:31:30.890
in Rodrigues' warehouse.

00:31:34.280 --> 00:31:34.870
Chief,

00:31:35.750 --> 00:31:38.280
according to Captain Huang's report,

00:31:38.430 --> 00:31:40.650
the underground anti-Japanese forces
in Macau

00:31:40.650 --> 00:31:43.250
are organizing the transport
of new supplies,

00:31:43.310 --> 00:31:46.100
and the quantity is unprecedented.

00:31:46.680 --> 00:31:49.000
What do you think we should do?

00:31:59.110 --> 00:32:00.110
Major Yamaguchi,

00:32:00.830 --> 00:32:01.800
well, this...

00:32:05.260 --> 00:32:07.000
Keep monitoring the situation first.

00:32:07.000 --> 00:32:08.900
I'll report to Chief later.

00:32:09.090 --> 00:32:09.660
Yes.

00:32:11.090 --> 00:32:11.920
Wait.

00:32:16.420 --> 00:32:17.000
Chief.

00:32:29.330 --> 00:32:30.440
There's a mission

00:32:33.100 --> 00:32:35.880
I need you to arrange right away.

00:32:36.900 --> 00:32:39.030
What is it? Please give me your orders.

00:33:03.000 --> 00:33:03.700
Chief,

00:33:03.960 --> 00:33:05.310
are you sure about this?

00:33:13.040 --> 00:33:14.020
Was I

00:33:16.990 --> 00:33:18.240
not clear enough?

00:33:22.420 --> 00:33:22.950
Yes.

00:33:23.970 --> 00:33:24.950
In this matter,

00:33:28.890 --> 00:33:30.210
I'll follow your instructions.

00:33:30.210 --> 00:33:31.070
I'll do my best.

00:33:43.620 --> 00:33:44.420
Consul,

00:33:45.020 --> 00:33:46.710
the early morning ship to Guangzhou

00:33:46.710 --> 00:33:49.400
will depart in one hour.

00:33:49.440 --> 00:33:51.460
The car is ready.

00:33:52.560 --> 00:33:55.900
This is a top-secret report for Command.

00:33:56.770 --> 00:33:57.690
Asahina,

00:33:58.300 --> 00:34:00.280
you're responsible for safekeeping it.

00:34:00.280 --> 00:34:00.910
Yes.

00:34:02.210 --> 00:34:03.010
Let's go.

00:34:39.659 --> 00:34:40.520
Consul!

00:35:03.300 --> 00:35:09.060
[Operating Room]

00:35:16.650 --> 00:35:17.880
Stand guard here

00:35:18.420 --> 00:35:19.680
and don't move an inch.

00:35:20.570 --> 00:35:22.760
I'll go report to Chief.

00:35:23.420 --> 00:35:23.920
Yes.

00:35:26.820 --> 00:35:27.300
Hello?

00:35:29.170 --> 00:35:29.790
Dr. Ke.

00:35:32.020 --> 00:35:32.690
What?

00:35:33.220 --> 00:35:35.150
Yasumitsu Fukae has been assassinated?

00:35:35.150 --> 00:35:37.390
This will be like an earthquake for Macau.

00:35:37.390 --> 00:35:38.480
Contact everyone immediately

00:35:38.480 --> 00:35:39.550
to prepare for contingencies.

00:35:39.550 --> 00:35:41.320
Especially regarding
the Portuguese Macau government,

00:35:41.320 --> 00:35:42.530
you must stay informed of the situation

00:35:42.530 --> 00:35:43.930
and try to keep them calm.

00:35:44.180 --> 00:35:45.870
Alright, I understand.

00:35:52.690 --> 00:35:54.070
Wang Qiuzai and Fearless Biao

00:35:54.070 --> 00:35:55.880
have been hidden
in my underground smoking room.

00:35:55.880 --> 00:35:57.780
That place is very secluded.

00:35:57.810 --> 00:35:59.650
Ordinary people would never find it.

00:35:59.650 --> 00:36:00.420
However...

00:36:03.380 --> 00:36:04.340
However what?

00:36:05.450 --> 00:36:06.780
Fearless Biao,

00:36:06.810 --> 00:36:08.540
when he grabbed the briefcase,

00:36:08.710 --> 00:36:11.440
seems to have been spotted
by Fukue's secretary.

00:36:12.290 --> 00:36:12.910
Just...

00:36:13.000 --> 00:36:13.980
Just a glimpse.

00:36:14.010 --> 00:36:15.470
It shouldn't be a problem.

00:36:18.050 --> 00:36:18.650
Hello?

00:36:27.060 --> 00:36:27.940
I got it.

00:36:29.250 --> 00:36:30.580
Keep watching closely.

00:36:31.200 --> 00:36:34.040
Report immediately if anything happens.

00:36:43.100 --> 00:36:45.300
Bring Fearless Biao back.

00:36:47.490 --> 00:36:48.190
Now?

00:36:49.400 --> 00:36:50.860
Yamaguchi just reported

00:36:52.000 --> 00:36:54.520
that Asahina has been taken to surgery.

00:36:55.440 --> 00:36:59.020
The hospital says
his injuries are very serious.

00:36:59.660 --> 00:37:01.790
There's little hope for his recovery.

00:37:02.540 --> 00:37:05.050
Wang Qiuzai is responsible
for reconnaissance.

00:37:05.050 --> 00:37:06.300
He can stay hidden.

00:37:06.600 --> 00:37:07.730
But Fearless Biao

00:37:08.240 --> 00:37:11.280
is the action team leader
of your Special Operations Team.

00:37:11.280 --> 00:37:13.530
He's always at the forefront
of everything.

00:37:13.530 --> 00:37:16.160
At a time like this, he can't be hiding.

00:37:16.890 --> 00:37:20.170
Otherwise, people might become
suspicious of him.

00:37:20.830 --> 00:37:21.350
Yes,

00:37:21.730 --> 00:37:23.460
I'll take care of it right away.

00:38:37.530 --> 00:38:38.330
Hello?

00:38:39.460 --> 00:38:40.730
Is it General Matsui?

00:38:41.430 --> 00:38:42.560
This is Sawa Eisaku.

00:38:45.340 --> 00:38:46.550
I have terrible news.

00:38:49.870 --> 00:38:51.000
Consul Fukue...

00:38:53.550 --> 00:38:54.820
Consul Fukue...

00:38:56.460 --> 00:38:57.220
Just now,

00:38:58.140 --> 00:38:59.450
he was killed!

00:39:01.310 --> 00:39:02.830
I'm sorry!

00:39:04.300 --> 00:39:06.180
I'm sorry!

00:39:08.690 --> 00:39:09.470
Yes!

00:39:10.180 --> 00:39:10.700
Yes.

00:39:12.270 --> 00:39:12.730
Yes.

00:39:45.610 --> 00:39:49.800
♪ City of joy ♪

00:39:49.800 --> 00:39:53.400
♪ City of love ♪

00:39:53.670 --> 00:39:57.670
♪ Paradise of dreams ♪

00:39:57.670 --> 00:40:01.420
♪ Flourishing Tokyo ♪

00:40:06.460 --> 00:40:07.120
This

00:40:07.150 --> 00:40:09.170
is the newly-received ultimatum

00:40:09.210 --> 00:40:11.380
from the Empire of Japan
to the Portuguese Government

00:40:11.380 --> 00:40:12.840
and the Macau government.

00:40:12.840 --> 00:40:16.240
It states that the assassination
of Yasumitsu Fukae

00:40:16.270 --> 00:40:19.520
is the greatest provocation
against the Empire of Japan.

00:40:20.490 --> 00:40:22.150
The Macau government bears

00:40:22.190 --> 00:40:23.980
undeniable responsibility for this.

00:40:23.980 --> 00:40:24.850
Therefore,

00:40:24.880 --> 00:40:26.800
the Japanese
Southern China Expeditionary Army

00:40:26.800 --> 00:40:30.210
has imposed a punitive blockade on Macau

00:40:30.210 --> 00:40:32.960
and reserves the right
to take further military action

00:40:32.960 --> 00:40:35.000
until the facts of this case are clarified

00:40:35.000 --> 00:40:37.840
and the perpetrator is properly punished.

00:40:38.130 --> 00:40:39.630
The Japanese side has appointed

00:40:39.630 --> 00:40:43.390
Keiichi Imai,
Deputy Consul General of Guangdong,

00:40:43.410 --> 00:40:46.010
to urgently take over
as the new consul in Macau

00:40:46.010 --> 00:40:46.940
and proceed to Macau,

00:40:46.940 --> 00:40:49.630
demanding that upon Consul Imai's arrival,

00:40:49.630 --> 00:40:51.780
he takes over all investigative authority
for this case.

00:40:51.780 --> 00:40:54.690
The Macau government and police
must fully cooperate

00:40:54.690 --> 00:40:57.090
without any interference or obstruction.

00:40:57.280 --> 00:41:00.600
Allowing the Japanese
to conduct investigations in Macau?

00:41:00.600 --> 00:41:03.770
This is an outright usurpation
of our judicial sovereignty!

00:41:03.770 --> 00:41:06.230
Exactly. This is absolutely unacceptable.

00:41:06.340 --> 00:41:08.870
How can we possibly let
the Japanese handle the investigations?

00:41:08.870 --> 00:41:10.730
The government should immediately
protest to Japan

00:41:10.730 --> 00:41:12.950
and demand they respect international law!

00:41:12.950 --> 00:41:13.800
Everyone!

00:41:14.800 --> 00:41:16.090
Look carefully.

00:41:16.360 --> 00:41:18.230
This is Japan's ultimatum

00:41:18.230 --> 00:41:20.030
with no room for negotiation.

00:41:20.030 --> 00:41:22.320
The Japanese are fully prepared

00:41:22.320 --> 00:41:24.650
to deploy troops to Macau at any moment.

00:41:24.650 --> 00:41:26.760
Accept it, or declare war.

00:41:26.760 --> 00:41:28.860
No other options!

00:41:34.940 --> 00:41:37.230
The immediate issue

00:41:37.250 --> 00:41:38.970
is that a foreign consul
has died in Macau.

00:41:38.970 --> 00:41:40.240
No matter what,

00:41:40.260 --> 00:41:42.510
we do bear some responsibility.

00:41:42.710 --> 00:41:44.960
The Japanese don't trust
the Macau government,

00:41:44.960 --> 00:41:47.430
and we have no choice
but to accept it now.

00:41:51.820 --> 00:41:52.670
Your Excellency the Governor,

00:41:52.670 --> 00:41:54.260
there's big trouble with the Fukue case.

00:41:54.260 --> 00:41:55.590
What has happened?

00:41:55.700 --> 00:41:57.270
The police have just found

00:41:57.300 --> 00:41:58.730
the abandoned vehicle
involved in the murder on the shore.

00:41:58.730 --> 00:42:01.360
Investigation shows
it belongs to Rodrigues' company.

00:42:01.360 --> 00:42:02.690
My company's car?

00:42:03.170 --> 00:42:04.960
Yes. Along with the car,

00:42:04.960 --> 00:42:07.280
your secretary Santos' body
was also found.

00:42:07.280 --> 00:42:10.390
One of the murder weapons
from the Fukue case was in his hand.

00:42:10.390 --> 00:42:11.520
Damn it.

00:42:11.880 --> 00:42:13.200
This is a frame-up.

00:42:13.510 --> 00:42:15.790
This is clearly a setup!

00:42:17.130 --> 00:42:18.360
Your Excellency the Governor,

00:42:18.360 --> 00:42:20.690
when will the new Japanese Consul arrive?

00:42:21.320 --> 00:42:23.670
Keiichi Imai has left Guangzhou

00:42:23.670 --> 00:42:25.800
and will arrive in Macau at 10 tonight.

00:42:29.550 --> 00:42:31.340
So in 5 more hours,

00:42:31.370 --> 00:42:32.510
the Japanese will take over

00:42:32.510 --> 00:42:33.570
the investigation of the Fukue case?

00:42:33.570 --> 00:42:34.050
Yes.

00:42:34.160 --> 00:42:36.000
I guess their first search target

00:42:36.000 --> 00:42:37.780
will definitely be my company
and warehouse.

00:42:37.780 --> 00:42:39.670
So we must act before then

00:42:39.690 --> 00:42:41.210
and quickly move these supplies

00:42:41.210 --> 00:42:42.000
into hiding.

00:42:43.590 --> 00:42:46.560
But my fleet has just arrived at the port.

00:42:46.730 --> 00:42:48.270
Now the entire Macau

00:42:48.300 --> 00:42:49.800
has been completely blockaded

00:42:49.800 --> 00:42:51.050
by the Japanese.

00:42:51.330 --> 00:42:53.300
The fleet can't leave at all now.

00:42:53.320 --> 00:42:56.050
Besides,
the quantity of goods is so large.

00:42:56.230 --> 00:42:57.870
Just unloading them

00:42:57.900 --> 00:42:59.450
took 2 whole days.

00:43:01.310 --> 00:43:02.760
In such a short time,

00:43:03.730 --> 00:43:04.900
how can we possibly transport everything?